{"tid":2344580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：拜登批評國防部拖延權力交接　令美國面臨安全風險","createTime":"2020-12-29T00:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:44:07.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08fbed827fd872726ebbe8cd49604474e4d2fb5a","tid":2344580,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:33:23.000Z","msg":"美國總統當選人拜登批評，<strong>國防部人員拖延權力交接工作，並警告將令美國面臨安全風險。</strong><br />\n<br />\n拜登與副總統當選人賀錦麗聽取交接小組的簡報後指出，<strong>他們的團隊面對國防部以及管理和預算辦公室障礙，無法獲得所需的重大安全資訊，認為這是不負責任。</strong><br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，他的團隊需要清楚了解美軍在世界各地的部署，防止被競爭對手利用作製造混亂。 他說，許多對美國安全至關重要的機構遭受了巨大破壞，許多人員的能力和士氣被挖空，不少政策進程受阻。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>國防部長埃斯珀在大選後不久被特朗普撤職</strong>，任命支持者米勒代理職務，被外界質疑<strong>企圖在總統任期最後階段製造混亂</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567561-20201229.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567561-20201229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=bf79241b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567561-20201229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b4cdff0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567561-20201229.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"cf7711f825d45d99a02dfa52208e87beb79aecf9","tid":2344580,"uid":26708,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"敗登"},{"pid":"a40e0faf479aa182c5e9a2fcd9403993cfbe2354","tid":2344580,"uid":30084,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:36:43.000Z","msg":"侵 : 拎到支棍先同我講野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f0db2fe36c79a1df032d33baeb0d1044d2f97a","tid":2344580,"uid":251736,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"冇武力，冇實權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"